# =============================================================================
# uDOS v1.1.9+ SHAKEDOWN TEST SUITE
# Comprehensive system validation using modern uPY syntax
# =============================================================================
#
# Tests:
#   1. Variables & Assignment
#   2. Functions & Return Values
#   3. Emoji Support
